saying my house was on fire.

00:14:44.600 --> 00:14:46.040
I left in a hurry,

00:14:46.320 --> 00:14:47.600
and the door wasn't closed tightly.

00:14:47.600 --> 00:14:48.260
As a result,

00:14:48.400 --> 00:14:50.240
some bastard made a prank call to me,

00:14:50.240 --> 00:14:51.680
saying my house wasn't on fire at all.

00:14:51.680 --> 00:14:51.940
Yes.

00:14:52.360 --> 00:14:53.360
Someone must have

00:14:53.520 --> 00:14:54.650
sneaked into my shop

00:14:54.760 --> 00:14:55.960
when I wasn't looking,

00:14:55.960 --> 00:14:57.320
and tampered with his car.

00:14:57.320 --> 00:14:58.040
Where are the security cameras?

00:14:58.040 --> 00:14:58.280
Uh.

00:14:58.600 --> 00:14:59.600
Yes, we have them.

00:14:59.960 --> 00:15:01.090
I have it on my phone.

00:15:09.480 --> 00:15:09.940
*Sigh.*

00:15:10.520 --> 00:15:11.200
Officer.

00:15:11.480 --> 00:15:12.280
N-now,

00:15:12.640 --> 00:15:14.100
do you believe what I said?

00:15:18.520 --> 00:15:20.250
Make a copy of this video for me.

00:15:21.040 --> 00:15:22.480
I'll contact you later if needed.

00:15:22.480 --> 00:15:22.680
Ah.

00:15:22.960 --> 00:15:23.720
Okay, okay.

00:15:24.120 --> 00:15:25.280
I'll copy it for you right now.

00:15:25.280 --> 00:15:26.080
Just a moment.

00:15:27.560 --> 00:15:30.420
Who do you think would mess with Zhao Wenbing's car?

00:15:31.920 --> 00:15:33.780
Besides that mysterious person,

00:15:33.840 --> 00:15:35.560
the people who most want him to have an accident

00:15:35.560 --> 00:15:36.560
are Xu Xing and Wang Min.